Class AndroidAarDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.AndroidAarDescription
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class AndroidAarDescription
extends Object
implements DescriptionWithTargetGraph<AndroidAarDescriptionArg>, ImplicitDepsInferringDescription<AndroidAarDescriptionArg>
    Description for a BuildRule that generates an .aar file.

    This represents an Android Library Project packaged as an .aar bundle as specified by: https://developer.android.com/studio/projects/android-library#aar-contents.

    Note that the aar may be specified as a SourcePath, so it could be either a binary .aar file checked into version control, or a zip file that conforms to the .aar specification that is generated by another build rule.
